== Welcome to MediaMaid
 
MediaMaid is an easy-to-use asset manager extension for Radiant CMS.
 
 
== Getting Started
 
 
[this will be procedure to install extension ]
 
1. Install ImageMagick. "Mac OS X":http://www.imagemagick.org/script/binary-releases.php#macosx


2. If you don't already have it, you'll need the paperclip gem

gem install paperclip

3. In your vendor/extensions directory, clone the code from github:

git clone git@github.com:blazingcloud/radiant-media-maid.git mediamaid

4. Run Radiant extension command-line functions:
rake radiant:extensions:mediamaid:migrate
rake radiant:extensions:mediamaid:update

5. Restart server
 
== Features
 
- resizes images to thumbnails
- access to gallery from single post admin pages